  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatumKeySelector<TDomainClass>
    Defines the interface to be implemented by the various datum key selection strategies.

    Named

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatumAuditor<TDomainClass>
    Keeps aggregated counts of the incoming reports and periodically produces corresponding breadcrumbs.
    DatumUtils
    A utility class for extracting various information provided via by the DatumType annotation.
    InMemoryEndPoint
    A special kind of EndPoint that allows clients to construct a pipeline where the DatumProducer produces into an in-memory end point and the DatumConsumerStream consumes data off of it.
    InMemoryEndPoints
    A helper class to easily manipulate InMemoryEndPoints.
